---
import PublicLayout from '../../layouts/PublicLayout.astro';
---

<PublicLayout
  title="Auto Detailing Services - ColorAuto"
  description="Comprehensive auto detailing in Grand Junction: hand wash, clay bar, interior deep clean, leather conditioning, wheels and tires."
  keywords={[
    'auto detailing Grand Junction',
    'interior detailing',
    'clay bar treatment',
    'car wash premium'
  ]}
  image="/images/autodetailing.jpg"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative text-white py-70 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="/images/autodetailing.jpg" alt="Auto Detailing" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4 drop-shadow-lg">Auto Detailing</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 drop-shadow-md">Professional car detailing to restore and protect your vehicle's appearance</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <!-- Left Column - Details -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Comprehensive Auto Detailing</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Our professional auto detailing service goes beyond a simple car wash. We meticulously clean, restore, and protect every surface of your vehicle to bring back that showroom shine.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-600">What's Included</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-lg">Professional Hand Wash</strong>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Using premium pH-balanced soaps and soft microfiber mitts to safely clean your paint</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-lg">Clay Bar Treatment</strong>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Removes embedded contaminants that washing alone can't eliminate</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-lg">Interior Deep Cleaning</strong>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Vacuum, steam clean, and condition all interior surfaces</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-lg">Leather Conditioning</strong>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Professional treatment to protect and preserve leather surfaces</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-xl mr-3">✓</span>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-lg">Wheel & Tire Care</strong>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Deep clean wheels, tires, and wheel wells with tire dressing</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Detailing Packages</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <!-- Interior -->
            <div class="border-b pb-4">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Interior Detailing</h4>
              </div>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Interior and trunk professionally vacuumed in every area to remove all traces of sand and dirt</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Carpets, seats, and floor mats steam cleaned or shampoo and extract</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Blow out and clean all vents</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>All plastic trim safely cleaned</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>All plastic trim protected in a satin, silicone free UV dressing – makes the interior look conditioned without the greasy look of cheap silicone dressings</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Interior glass thoroughly cleaned</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Door jams and rubber seals cleaned</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <!-- Exterior -->
            <div class="border-b pb-4">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Exterior Detailing</h4>
              </div>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Chemical decontamination of wheels and brakes and agitated with a variety of wheel brushes – removes baked on brake dust</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Tires, door jams degreased and agitated with a variety of detailing brushes – dissolves built up grime, silicone oils and dirt accumulation</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Tar and bug splatter sprayed with a concentrated cleaning agent – safely dissolves contamination to allow for gentle cleaning</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Entire vehicle thoroughly washed with 2 bucket wash method and clayed – removes embedded contamination from paint for a smooth finish through the use of an automotive clay bar and lubricant</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Paintwork lightly polished/waxed – improves gloss levels of the paintwork and can hide minor paint imperfection (not proper paint correction like in other packages)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Hand wash using only microfiber towels</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Clay bar to decontaminate paint</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Clean door jams</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Clean wheels and wheel wells</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>UV protectant applied to trim</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>3-4 month synthetic wax protection</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <!-- Full Auto -->
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
                <h4 class="font-bold text-lg">Full Auto Detailing</h4>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">Includes both the exterior and interior detail plus the vehicle's engine bay is cleaned.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-blue-200">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-base mb-3">Additional Auto Detailing Charges</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Paint Correction (requires visual inspection for exact quote)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                <span>Upgrade to Premium Paint Sealant for 6-8 months of protection for $85</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-6">*Pricing varies by vehicle size and condition</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column - Image & CTA -->
      <div>
        <div class="bg-gray-200 rounded-lg h-96 mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
          <img src="/images/professional auto detailing.jpg" alt="Auto Detailing Service" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg" />
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Restore Your Vehicle?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            Contact us today for a free quote and to schedule your detailing appointment.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="block w-full bg-blue-600 text-white text-center font-bold py-3 rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition mb-3">
            Get a Free Quote
          </a>
          <a href="tel:970-628-1505" class="block w-full bg-gray-800 text-white text-center font-bold py-3 rounded hover:bg-gray-900 transition">
            Call: 970-628-1505
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">Why Choose ColorAuto?</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>✓ Experienced professional detailers</li>
            <li>✓ Premium products and equipment</li>
            <li>✓ Satisfaction guarantee</li>
            <li>✓ Convenient Grand Junction location</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Other Services -->
  <section class="bg-white py-12">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-10">Other Services</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Hand Wash</h3>
            <span class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-700">$45+</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Premium hand wash with pH-balanced care.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-green-600 mr-2">•</span><span>Premium hand wash with pH-balanced soap</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-green-600 mr-2">•</span><span>Wheels cleaned</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-green-600 mr-2">•</span><span>Exterior windows</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-green-600 mr-2">•</span><span>Towel and compressed air dried</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-4">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Maintenance Detail</h3>
            <span class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-700">$125+</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Everything in Hand Wash plus added protection and interior care.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-green-600 mr-2">•</span><span>Everything in the Hand Wash</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-green-600 mr-2">•</span><span>Spray wax</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-green-600 mr-2">•</span><span>Vacuum carpets, seats, and floor mats</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-green-600 mr-2">•</span><span>Wipe down and dust interior plastic trim</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-green-600 mr-2">•</span><span>Interior windows</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related Services -->
  <section class="bg-gray-100 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Enhance Your Detailing</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <a href="/services/ceramic-coating" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-blue-600">Ceramic Coating</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Add long-lasting protection and shine</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/paint-protection-film" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-blue-600">Paint Protection Film</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Shield against chips and scratches</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/services/window-tinting" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow hover:shadow-lg transition text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-blue-600">Window Tinting</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">UV protection and privacy</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PublicLayout>
               
